{"data":{"post":{"id":"a0a322b0-2668-5607-9d59-84c84961d43b","html":"<p><figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/ab0e7/communicate.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.94117647058823%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"communicate\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/78f2b/communicate.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/dce19/communicate.jpg 200w,\n/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/c1413/communicate.jpg 400w,\n/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/78f2b/communicate.jpg 800w,\n/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/ab0e7/communicate.jpg 1020w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure></p>\n<h3>你在工作中遇到过沟通问题吗?</h3>\n<p><em>1. 是否在某个周一的上午，遇到过让你抓狂的沟通者?</em><br>\n<em>2. 有没有在某次会议上，有过拍桌子的冲动?</em><br>\n<em>3. 工作中,面对无法沟通的对象,该如何处理?</em><br>\n…… </p>\n<p>从小我们被教育:好好说话。但是，没有人给我们定义: 什么是好好说话，要什么样的表情，什么样的语气，哪些话，该如何说?<br>\n如果你在大公司就职，作为新员工，可能会接收“软技能”培训。但在大公司内部还是经常看到办公室拍桌子，扯着嗓子对撕。<br>\n其实，人生就是一场修行，何况生活在xx都已经很苦了，何必为难对方。</p>\n<p>然而，世界上没有如果，不是所有人都会换位思考。 </p>\n<h4>职场中,如何沟通，才能最高效果?</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>首先,得听出来:对方要干嘛?<br>\n区分三个概念: <strong>行动、利益、需求</strong>。需求演变不同的利益，然后我们会选择不同的行动计划去满足这些需求和利益。   </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>透过情绪, 找到未达成一致的原因到底在哪里?<br>\n对方有情绪的根本原因是什么?<br>\n他的根因到底在哪里?<br>\n哪些需求未满足?    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>表达自己的感受, 清楚的表达自己的愿望。 </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>达成一致后，跟踪行动及目标实现进展，跟踪实施均做到闭环(最好邮件存档)。  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>心存感激。\n感谢他人的行为提升了我们的生活品质。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>沟通是最常见、最重要的日常活动，不仅仅是与同事的沟通、领导的沟通，同样重要的是与家人的沟通、朋友的沟通。<br>\n我们是否仅仅作为观察者，不带批评与评论，在为我们努力达成的目标而陈述事实依据—>表达感受+愿望。</p>\n<h3>善待自己，善待他人。</h3>\n<p><figure>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/22484/0828_yoga.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"0828 yoga\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/78f2b/0828_yoga.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/dce19/0828_yoga.jpg 200w,\n/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/c1413/0828_yoga.jpg 400w,\n/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/78f2b/0828_yoga.jpg 800w,\n/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/ab4c4/0828_yoga.jpg 1200w,\n/static/aa7daa287ac5cd138b4582599faedc0c/22484/0828_yoga.jpg 1224w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    <figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">unsplash.com</figcaption></figure></p>","fields":{"slug":"/communicate-with-someone/","prefix":"2018-08-28"},"frontmatter":{"title":"How do you communicate at work?","author":"Jane","category":"thought","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/7767b78d744d59e457fe61e5ab890392/ada8c/communicate.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"e6ec6ad4-4c6b-586c-bfdf-8cdf2d09548f","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/communicate-with-someone/","prev":{"id":"e2dccbb4-7223-537d-9127-fbd41d07f454","fields":{"slug":"/Compound-interest/","prefix":"2018-08-23","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Do you know \"compound interest\"?","category":"thought"}},"next":{"id":"0bef48b7-5fe8-5dbc-bf23-a2518b6cf94c","fields":{"slug":"/who-are-you/","prefix":"2018-08-30","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Who are you?","category":"thought"}},"source":"posts"}}